content: Aigccoin is a decentralized platform for digital currency, global payments, and running smart contracts, originating from Ethereum. Aigccoin consists of cryptocurrency (AIGC), blockchain ledger, and the application and service ecosystem running on top of it. Aigccoin integrates generative artificial intelligence (AI) capabilities, aiming to provide decentralized, secure, and trustworthy AI applications and services.- Website  https://aigccoin.org/- Github   https://github.com/aigccoin- Client    https://github.com/aigccoin/go-aigccoin/releases- Wallet   https://medium.com/@aigccoin/tutorial-set-up-aigccoin-wallet-85781af6f7b9- Twitter   https://twitter.com/AigccoinOrg- Discord https://discord.gg/SXA2vWxbxk- Pool      https://github.com/aigccoin/open-ethereum-pool/releases- Miner    https://github.com/NebuTech/NBMiner- Explorer http://explorer.aigccoin.org/Mining information:- Genesis Block Time: 2023-6-27- Block Rewards:  20000 AIGC- Blocking Speed:  20 seconds- Maximum supply: unlimited supply- Core Algorithm:  Ethash
